This paper deals with statistical characterization of a fading channel, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), and networking (cs.NI). The paper also applies the results to the performance analysis of wireless communication systems, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.MA).
